Package: PowerFrechetMeanR
Title: Power Frechet Mean in Euclidean Spaces
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R:
    person("Chris", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "chris@uber.space")
Description: Computes the power Frechet mean in Euclidean space. Given n data
    points in R^d and a power parameter a > 0, the power Frechet mean
    minimises the sum of a-th powers of Euclidean distances to a query point.
    The objective and gradient are implemented in C++ via RcppArmadillo and
    optimised with L-BFGS-B. Special cases include the arithmetic mean (a = 2)
    and the geometric median (a = 1).
